## TurtleBot3 From Robotis

* Small 3 wheeled Robot
* Many manufacturers
* Ours come from Robotis
* See [Robotis Turtlebot3](http://emanual.robotis.com/docs/en/platform/turtlebot3/overview/)
* We assemble them
* Cost around $500
* Two powered wheels, and one caster wheel
* Powered wheels
  * Dynamixel motors
  * "Smart" motors
* [OpenCR board](http://emanual.robotis.com/docs/en/parts/controller/opencr10/)
  * Arduino compatible
  * Will accept Arduino add-on boards
  * Motor controller
  * Pre-programmed
  * Includes
    * Gyroscope 3Axis
    * Accelerometer 3Axis
    * Magnetometer 3Axis (MPU9250)
* [Raspberry Pi SBC)
  * Single Board Computer
  * Full Linux!
  * Connects to the OpenCR


 